{"tid":1092912,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"衲誆2女信徒「陰陽雙修」　私生活淫亂全曝光","createTime":"2019-04-05T08:15:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-05T09:21:18.000Z","uid":234553,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"7c14cf4aec47e6fcb10fc79b609ec6d8038179c6","tid":1092912,"uid":234553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T08:15:22.000Z","msg":"色即是空，空即是色！越南一名道貌岸然的和尚，被網友爆料和女信徒「全裸雙修」，多張照片曝光後，引發大批佛教信徒的不滿，目前相關單位已經介入調查中。<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2019/04/05/1861386-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2019%2F04%2F05%2F1861386-XXL.jpg&h=1a6ec04f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▼▲越南和尚與女信徒雙修。（圖／翻攝自《中國報》）<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2019/04/05/1861387-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2019%2F04%2F05%2F1861387-XXL.jpg&h=81cb8c20&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n據馬來西亞《中國報》報導，在外人眼裡看來，平時身穿袈裟的越南和尚令人尊敬，但卻被網友爆料私生活淫亂，多張淫穢照片也隨之曝光，照片中和尚分別和兩名身穿碎花洋裝、紅色上衣的女信徒「陰陽雙修」，如此嚴重違反紀律和法律的行為，讓大批佛教信徒相當不滿，越南當局也已經介入調查中，將嚴格懲戒該名和尚。<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2019/04/05/1861388-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2019%2F04%2F05%2F1861388-XXL.jpg&h=f35f1351&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▼▲越南和尚與女信徒雙修，違反當地紀律和法律。（圖／翻攝自《中國報》）<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2019/04/05/1861389-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2019%2F04%2F05%2F1861389-XXL.jpg&h=68fa5f3e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n過度迷信害慘自己，中國大陸廣東省肇慶市德慶縣也曾發生過類似事件，一名自稱大師的劉姓男子謊稱「露奶能治病」，女信徒被要求掀起上衣，任由他胡亂揉胸，過程中劉男拿著香，嘴裡還念念有詞。當地村民表示，「用我的眼光來看，那是封建迷信，都是一種心裡安慰，哪有什麼功效啊！」就連看過影片的網友也笑回「順便揉揉腦子吧」、「還有這麼傻的人？法師能治病？」<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2019/04/05/1861390-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2019%2F04%2F05%2F1861390-XXL.jpg&h=28c5bc2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲越南和尚與女信徒雙修，違反當地紀律和法律。（圖／翻攝自《中國報》）"},{"pid":"4bf104f60c375ccd519ff16900b6b3dc1b02b07d","tid":1092912,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T08:33:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b67a24f28232706df6263f216dad8de6c37bb66","tid":1092912,"uid":20658,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T08:35:58.000Z","msg":"2019啦仲有傻西信呢啲人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68c00c749cba0015d266ed427a94acee16d5f157","tid":1092912,"uid":121546,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T08:36:29.000Z","msg":"練緊密宗瑜珈姐<br />\n歡樂佛都支持男女雙修架"},{"pid":"34f21df6e0b24d3f053e07fdfca77878756eee1d","tid":1092912,"uid":59832,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T08:37:12.000Z","msg":"@老衲-"},{"pid":"315a8b088e758f98cf6c4d3b41071623dd868bb2","tid":1092912,"uid":43483,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T08:42:19.000Z","msg":"和尚都勁過連登仔有得扑野<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bce7d3f3ee7b607fa0c9e159274fa2030d636eb","tid":1092912,"uid":51753,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T09:02:16.000Z","msg":"老納的棒子<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89ae8f853e57551e947ff4284376867b9d1eeadf","tid":1092912,"uid":62506,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T09:08:23.000Z","msg":"點解扑野唔可以修行，性交唔可以轉運先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aac2b7281e761b13861c19294228323aaf07d07d","tid":1092912,"uid":185142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T09:08:32.000Z","msg":"我要求好簡單<br />\n<br />\n無格相，女信徒樣"},{"pid":"24aa24de7b1d5ed5613855aa19c918426d631db0","tid":1092912,"uid":62506,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":